data.description: This updated colonial home offers the perfect blend of classic charm and modern convenience. As you step inside, you'll immediately notice the attention to detail and thoughtful renovations. The first floor features a convenient laundry room, bathroom and bedroom. The kitchen has been tastefully updated with modern appliances, creating a chef's dream. Moving through the home, you'll find a cozy living area with plenty of natural light. The layout seamlessly blends the common areas, allowing for an open concept feel while still providing designated spaces for all your daily activities. Upstairs, three generously-sized bedrooms offer a peaceful retreat. Each room is thoughtfully designed to maximize comfort and functionality, accommodating your personal needs and preferences. With its traditional charm, modern amenities, and ideal location, this updated colonial home is truly a gem. Don't miss the opportunity to make it yours!
